============== HOW TO MAKE VIEW PANE (BROWSER) SCREENSHOTS: ===================================
1-METHOD:

element = context.driver.find_element(By.TAG_NAME, 'body')
element.screenshot("screenshot_full.png")


"creenshot_full.png" - THIS FILE WILL BE GENERATED into my framework after shooting



2-METHOD:

element = driver.find_element_by_tag_name('body')
element_png = element.screenshot_as_png
with open("test1.png", "wb") as file:
file.write(element_png)


"test1.png" - THIS FILE WILL BE GENERATED into my framework after shooting